;; ooyake 公 — gov-units.world-foreign.edn
;;
;; REAL DATA — world foreign-affairs ministries (executive diplomatic layer). Per
;; founder directive to raise coverage to 全世界政府. One-time maintainer pull of the
;; Wikidata SPARQL endpoint 2026-06-03: items instance-of (P31) "foreign affairs
;; ministry" (wd:Q20901295), not dissolved (no P576), whose country (P17) is one
;; already in the atlas (a current UN member), + official site (P856). Exact QIDs
;; from the SPARQL JSON (no summarizing model). Multi-entity countries → one chosen
;; deterministically. Countries whose foreign ministry is ALREADY in the atlas (e.g.
;; Japan's 外務省 gov.jpn.mofa) are skipped — no duplicate QID.
;;
;; COVERAGE HONESTY (G5): not every country's foreign ministry is typed Q20901295 on
;; Wikidata; untyped/differently-typed ones are NOT fabricated. :level :ministry,
;; :branch :executive, parent = gov.<iso>. Every row :authoritative +
;; :maintainer-verified. :official-url / :provenance = the ministry's OWN site (P856)
;; else the Wikidata entity. Observational mirror (G3/G11). Live ingest + publication
;; remain operator/Council steps.

